snippet.title: El Paso, Elsewhere Animated Music Video - STAY AWAKE
snippet.description:
Check out the official animated music video for STAY AWAKE, from the El Paso, Elsewhere soundtrack! El Paso, Elsewhere is a third-person love letter to classic shooters releasing September 26th, 2023 on PC and Xbox. Neo-noir never looked so good.

STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1546310/
